Afterwards with tears she raised a tomb and eon- secrated his ashes. Weep no more for this great blessing! He has attained to the realms of heaven, yet none the less he moves over the earth and does not leave this world. He still discourses, still holds forth, expounding‚ teaching, instructing‚ prophesy- ing3 and not only does he direct the peoples of Libya, but goes forth to the east and the west, nur- turing the Gauls, training the Britons, keeping guard over Italy, spreading the knowledge of Christ in farthest Spain.
